EQUINOID

Equinoids are horse-like humanoids with exceptional speed and endurance.
Their Spd attribute is among the highest of any OCC-eligible race.  They
tend toward warrior and outdoorsman roles.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 6-16   ME: 3-18   MA: 3-18   PS: 8-28 (Supernatural)
  PP: 3-18   PE: 8-28   PB: 3-18   Spd: 15-40

DAMAGE POOL:
  SDC: 3d6 x10 (approx 30-180)

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance
  - Exceptional Spd: among the fastest of playable races
  - Hooves as natural weapons

PENALTIES:
  - Hooved feet limit some equipment options
  - D-Bee status in Coalition territory

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

See also: coyle, kankoran, races
